        <h1 class="heading-large">Roadmap</h1>
            <p>Here’s a list of the new functionality we’re planning to offer through GOV.UK&nbsp;Pay.</p>

            <p class="panel panel-border-wide">This roadmap is a only a guide and may change from month to month.</p>

            <h2 class="heading-small">July-September</h2>
              <ul class="list list-bullet">
                <li>Improved onboarding experience</li>
                <li>Self service account creation and team management</li>
                <li>Support for Barclays ePDQ payment gateway</li>
                <li>Improved refund-related reporting</li>
              </ul>

            <h2 class="heading-small">September onwards</h2>
              <ul class="list list-bullet">
                <li>Improved reporting for bank reconciliation</li>
                <li>Support for Maestro and Visa Electron</li>
                <li>Foreign currency support</li>
                <li>Foreign language support</li>
                <li>Direct Debit functionality</li>
                <li>Support for eWallets</li>
                <li>Telephone payment functionality</li>
              </ul>

            <h2 class="heading-medium">Queries and suggestions</h2>
            <p>If you want to find out more about these features, or have some needs that GOV.UK Pay isn’t yet meeting, please get in touch with us by emailing <a href="mailto:govuk-pay-support@digital.cabinet-office.gov.uk">govuk-pay-support@digital.cabinet-office.gov.uk</a> or chat with us in our <a href="https://ukgovernmentdigital.slack.com/messages/govuk-pay">cross-government Slack channel</a>.</p>
